## Real-World Applications

Our software systems research improves how companies build and operate software:

- **Cloud Computing**: Scalable cloud architectures and distributed systems
- **Distributed Systems**: Consensus algorithms and fault-tolerant systems
- **DevOps Automation**: Continuous integration and deployment pipelines
- **Software Testing**: Automated testing and quality assurance techniques
- **Database Optimization**: Query optimization and data management

## Current Projects

- Microservices architecture patterns and best practices
- Serverless computing optimization and observability
- Container orchestration and resource management
- Software testing at massive scale
- Database query optimization for analytical workloads

## Industry Partnerships

We collaborate with major cloud providers and software companies to ensure our research addresses real-world challenges. Many of our findings influence industry standards and best practices.
